http://www.eui.eu/Documents/DepartmentsCentres/Law/Professors/Scheinin/ConsolidatedWorldCour
tStatute.pdf. 
</p>
<p> 69  A/HRC/19/NGO/124, http://www.internationalbillofrights.org/. 
 70  Joost Pauwelyn, &#8220;A World Environment Court&#8221;, <i>International Environmental Governance (Gaps and 
</i></p>
